## Domain Specific Information
- The Sugar Maple (Acer saccharum) species typically has leaves with lengths between 4-8 cm and widths between 3-6 cm, with a slightly narrower shape.
- The Red Maple (Acer rubrum) species typically has leaves with lengths between 3-6 cm and widths between 2-5 cm, with a more oval shape.
- The Silver Maple (Acer saccharinum) species typically has leaves with lengths between 5-10 cm and widths between 4-8 cm, with a more elliptical shape.
