- Convolutional Neural Networks (CNNs) to classify images of leaves.
- Natural Language Processing (NLP) techniques to analyze text-based descriptions of leaves.
- Support Vector Machines (SVMs) to classify leaves based on a non-linear kernel.

## Evaluation Metrics
The performance of the task model can be evaluated using metrics such as accuracy, precision, recall, and F1-score.

## Additional Notes
